pageProduct.name: Nutra-Life Probiotica Extra Care 14 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

A 14 day high strength, short course of probiotics to helps support gastrointestinal health during and after an antibiotic course

Suitable For: Vegans and vegetarians

Size: 14C

KEY FEATURES

• High Strength, Short Course Probiotic
• 75 Billion Good Bacteria, 6 strains

Ingredients

Contains: Contains: Sorbates, sulphites

Allergen Free From: Artificial Colours| Artificial Flavours| Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Soy| Wheat

Directions

RECOMMENDED DOSAGE: Take 1 capsule daily with food, or as directed by your healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store in a cool, dry place below 25°C.
